Hey, octopus car!

57
00:08:08,764 --> 00:08:10,855
Your car looks
like a red octopus!

58
00:08:10,975 --> 00:08:12,282
Hey, fuckhead!

59
00:08:14,071 --> 00:08:15,908
I'll give you a good beating!

60
00:08:20,406 --> 00:08:22,034
