He's having a bath.
You should go, too.

67
00:10:23,186 --> 00:10:24,543
Chibi, dinner time.

68
00:10:25,184 --> 00:10:26,146
Come here.

69
00:10:27,564 --> 00:10:29,501
Just a second.

70
00:11:03,590 --> 00:11:07,296
<i>MARU</i>

71
